header.questionMarkInfo:
Elspot prices represent the result of Nord Pool Spot’s day ahead implicit auction market. 

 

Peak = 08:00 to 20:00

Off peak 1 = 00:00 to 08:00

Off peak 2 = 20:00 to 00:00

Average = arithmetic average
header.description: Changes in the Norwegian bidding areas can affect which geographical area the city references refer to. Please see the area change log pdf.
